OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784906303
OL,3,CNHS in North East urges young people
OL,4,Cto get vaccinated against Meningitis B
OL,6,FThe NHS in the North East is urging
OL,7,Fstudents to take up a free vaccine
OL,8,Fagainst Meningitis B (MenB) before
OL,9,Fthousands head off to university this
OL,10,FSeptember.
OL,12,FA one-off programme of jabs is being
OL,13,Frolled out from this week, offering
OL,14,Fprotection against the rare but
OL,15,Fserious bacterial infection.
OL,17,FIt follows a concerning rise in MenB
OL,18,Fcases earlier this year, including a
OL,19,Fcluster centered in the Kent area.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
