PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784906303
OL,3,CNHS in North East urges young people
OL,4,Cto get vaccinated against Meningitis B
OL,6,FThe bacteria is spread through close
OL,7,Fcontact, including sharing drinks or
OL,8,Fvapes, and living in shared
OL,9,Faccommodation.
OL,11,FThousands of young people across the
OL,12,Fregion are eligible for the free
OL,13,Fvaccine, including:
OL,15,FTwo doses are needed, given four weeks
OL,16,Fapart, which is why NHS bosses are
OL,17,Furging young people to book their
OL,18,Fvaccines as soon as possible, to
OL,19,Fensure the protection kicks in before
OL,20,Fthey head to university.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
