OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784906303
OL,3,CNHS in North East urges young people
OL,4,Cto get vaccinated against Meningitis B
OL,6,FThe campaign is being backed by Joanne
OL,7,FBolam from Newcastle, whose 19-year-
OL,8,Fold son Jack died within 48 hours
OL,9,Fafter falling ill from Meningitis B.
OL,11,FShe told ITV News Tyne Tees: "I urge
OL,12,Fpeople to get vaccinated, especially
OL,13,Fthose off to uni. It's just the tip of
OL,14,Fthe iceberg, the criteria options need
OL,15,Fto be widely available for young
OL,16,Fpeople who like to mix, not just at
OL,17,Funiversity."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784906303
OL,3,CNHS in North East urges young people
OL,4,Cto get vaccinated against Meningitis B
OL,6,FJoanne added that Jack would not have
OL,7,Fbeen eligible for the vaccination
OL,8,Frollout as he was not a university
OL,9,Fstudent, but still contracted the
OL,10,Fvirus.
OL,12,FBen Anderson, director of population
OL,13,Fhealth, NHS North East and North
OL,14,FCumbria Integrated Care Board (ICB),
OL,15,Fsaid: "Although MenB is uncommon, it
OL,16,Fcan become life-threatening incredibly
OL,17,Fquickly. This vaccine offers young
OL,18,Fpeople the best protection at exactly
OL,19,Fthe time they need it most.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
