OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784906303
OL,3,CNHS in North East urges young people
OL,4,Cto get vaccinated against Meningitis B
OL,6,F"We're encouraging everyone who is
OL,7,Feligible to have their vaccines,
OL,8,Fbefore they start university so they
OL,9,Fcan begin the academic year protected
OL,10,Fagainst a disease that can have
OL,11,Fdevastating consequences."
OL,13,FSymptoms of MenB can appear suddenly
OL,14,Fand include a high temperature, severe
OL,15,Fheadache, vomiting, stiff neck,
OL,16,Fconfusion and a rash that doesn't fade
OL,17,Funder pressure.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
