PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1784906303
OL,3,CNHS in North East urges young people
OL,4,Cto get vaccinated against Meningitis B
OL,6,FAround one in 10 cases is fatal, while
OL,7,Fsurvivors can be left with life-
OL,8,Fchanging disabilities including
OL,9,Famputations, hearing loss and brain
OL,10,Fdamage.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/6
